userStories.notes:
The RetroUI Select component is already available at platform/browser-extension/src/side-panel/components/retro/Select.tsx — do NOT recreate it. Import it with: import { Select } from './retro/Select.js';

The PermissionSelect should be defined in ToolRow.tsx and exported alongside ToolRow so both PluginCard and BrowserToolsCard can import it.

The compact sizing is critical — the default RetroUI Select has h-10 min-w-40 which is too large for tool rows. Override with className on Select.Trigger: 'h-6 w-[4.5rem] min-w-0 px-1.5 py-0 font-mono text-xs shadow-none focus:shadow-[2px_2px_0_0_var(--color-border)]'.
